channel.title: Webclient Tutorials
channel.description: I know there has been several tutorials on how to jar a client and place it into an HTML webpage and onto a website. I own my own web hosting and website design company so hosting is no issue for me. My issue is finding a complete enough tutorial, and yes i have searched for it. Most searches came up missing or just idiot posts. Does anyone know of a tutorial better than [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,336494.0.html]Ric's Web Client Tutorial[/url]?
